fields.title: Goat Gene Optimizer
fields.description:
Produces genetically enhanced goats with a special machine that modifies the goat's genetic material prior to implantation. We need an interface for the machine that will display different characteristics the breeder might want to enhance.

The interface needs to be impressive, because the machine doesn't actually work, obviously.
fields.applicant_requirements: Applicants must be able to keep a straight face while producing absolute nonsense.
